==Introduction==
対潜水艦に使用する増加爆雷装備です。<br>
駆逐艦や海防艦などに爆雷投射機やソナー類などの対潜装備ともに装備することで、対潜能力の向上が図れます。

''This is additional depth charge equipment used for anti-submarine warfare.''<br>
''Equipping it together with other ASW equipment such as depth charge projectors or sonars on destroyers, coastal defense ships and the like can increase their anti-submarine capabilities.''

==Notes==
Ships receive a boost of 15% more ASW firepower when this is used together with a [[:Category:SONAR|SONAR]], 10% when used with only a [[:Category:Depth Charge Projectors|depth charge projectors]], and 43% more power when used with both a [[:Category:SONAR|SONAR]] and a [[:Category:Depth Charge Projectors|depth charge projectors]] (must be on the same ship). The 43% bonus does not apply when combined with any of the [[:Category:Special Depth Charge Projectors|special DCPs]]. Only the 15% bonus will apply.

